            "family": {
                "name": "Elemental, Earth",
                "type": "monster_family",
                "sections": [
                    {
                        "name": "Diverse Elementals",
                        "type": "section",
                        "text": "The Elemental Planes are more than expanses of sky, rock, metal fire, wood, and ocean. Clouds of fog, dust, and storms float through the Plane of Air. The Plane of Earth includes verdant groves, shining metal and crystal, and irradiated wastelands. The Plane of Fire features magma, suffocating smoke, and radiant firelight. Amid the endless sea of the Plane of Water are pockets of ooze and brine, plus the otherworldly environs of the deep.",
                        "sources": [
                            {
                                "type": "source",
                                "name": "Monster Core",
                                "link": {
                                    "type": "link",
                                    "name": "Monster Core pg. 142",
                                    "alt": "Monster Core pg. 142",
